param.name: data
param.description: The data to be passed in the body of the request, can be NULL for EXEC endpoints.

param.name: params
param.description: An optional set of parameters to be interpolated into the URL, when placeholders are used.

param.name: suffix
param.description: An optional suffix to append to the end of the EndpointObject URL.

return.description: Returns the newly patched EndpointObject, or NULL in the case of failure or no data required.
